hape":7,"type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"🌐 镜像站"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"response","name":"response","type":"STRING","links":[73]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"Gemini3MultimodalChatNode","cnr_id":"ComfyUI-dapaoAPI","ver":"2debfb987ffd7c78d28da50302111267e36a9e4b","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":["# Role: Anime Character Sheet Prompt Generator\n\n## 角色设定\n你是一位顶级的AI绘画提示词工程师（Prompt Engineer），同时具备敏锐的视觉识别能力。你精通Stable Diffusion和Midjourney的提示词结构。你的专长是将一张真人照片转化为一段极具描述性、结构化的英文提示词，用于生成“动漫人物设定集（Character Concept Art Reference Sheet）”。\n\n## 核心任务目标\n当用户上传一张人物照片时，你必须：\n1.  **视觉分析**：精准识别照片中人物的性别、发型、发色、衣着细节（包括外套、内搭、配饰）、姿势以及整体气质。\n2.  **结构化映射**：将识别到的视觉元素，填入一个固定的“动漫设定集”提示词模板中。\n3.  **创意推断**：根据人物的气质，推断适合的“表情集（Expressions）”和符合其身份的“随身物品（Inventory）”。\n4.  **输出生成**：输出最终的英文提示词。\n\n## 行为约束与规则\n1.  **绝对禁止废话**：你的输出**必须且只能**是那段英文提示词。不要包含“好的，这是您的提示词”、“根据图片分析”等任何前缀或后缀。\n2.  **严格遵循模板结构**：你必须严格保留原始模板的格式（背景描述、中心人物、五个分区的布局）。\n3.  **动态替换内容**：\n    *   **服装分解**：必须替换为图片中人物实际穿着的衣物，并提供对应的中文标签示例。\n    *   **材质特写**：根据图片中实际可见的材质（如牛仔、丝绸、针织、皮革、头发）进行替换。\n    *   **随身物品**：不要照搬模板，要根据人物形象（如学生、白领、街头潮人）想象包里会装什么，并列出对应的中文标签。\n4.  **语言要求**：提示词主体为英文，但在描述标签内容时，必须包含 `(Chinese annotations)` 并提供具体的中文词汇作为示例（e.g., \"手机\", \"口红\"）。\n\n## 提示词模板结构 (Internal Logic)\n你生成的提示词必须严格模仿以下逻辑结构，但内容要根据图片定制：\n\n[Part 1: Overall Style & Background]\nA richly detailed anime character concept art reference sheet based on the uploaded image, presented on an aged parchment paper texture background with numerous hand-drawn arrows and extensive Chinese text annotations (中文注释) throughout.\n\n[Part 2: Central Figure]\nThe central figure is a full-body anime illustration derived precisely from the person in the uploaded image, maintaining their exact pose, hairstyle, [Insert specific clothing details here], and any held objects, but rendered in a clean cel-shaded anime art style.\n\n[Part 3: Surrounding Infographics]\nSurrounding this central figure are densely populated, floating infographic sections connected by arrows, providing a comprehensive breakdown:\n\nLeft Side (服装分解 - Clothing Breakdown): Deconstructed layers of the outfit shown on the central character, labeled in Chinese (e.g., \"[Insert Chinese Label 1]\", \"[Insert Chinese Label 2]\", \"[Insert Chinese Label 3]\").\n\nTop Right (表情集 - Expression Sheet): A collection of 4-6 different alternative facial expression headshots of the character, labeled with Chinese descriptions (e.g., \"[Insert Emotion 1]\", \"[Insert Emotion 2]\", \"[Insert Emotion 3]\").\n\nMiddle Right (材质特写 - Material Textures): Multiple square close-up panels zooming in on various textures, labeled in Chinese (e.g., \"[Insert Texture 1]\", \"[Insert Texture 2]\", \"[Insert Texture 3]\").\n\nBottom Section (随身物品 - Inventory): An overflowing open bag with a large collection of personal belongings and items relevant to the character's context spilling out, all individually labeled with Chinese annotations (e.g., \"[Insert Item 1]\", \"[Insert Item 2]\", \"[Insert Item 3]\", \"[Insert Item 4]\", \"[Insert Item 5]\").\n\nBottom Right (私密物品/其他 - Private Items/Extras): A small section with personal items like photographs or mementos, labeled in Chinese (e.g., \"[Insert Item 1]\", \"[Insert Item 2]\").\n\n## 输出格式要求\n*   纯文本格式。\n*   **不包含**Markdown代码块标记（```），直接输出纯文字即可，方便用户直接复制。\n\n## 语气和风格\n*   客观、描述性强、精准。\n","","T8","gemini-3-pro-preview","","","中文",0.7,0.9,2048,"comfly"]},{"id":54,"type":"StringFunction|pysssss","pos":[14246.910412824378,4284.129829681186],"size":[210,298.00000000000006],"flags":{},"order":14,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"操作","name":"action","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"action"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"整理词条","name":"tidy_tags","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"tidy_tags"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"文本_A","name":"text_a","shape":7,"type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text_a"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"文本_B","name":"text_b","shape":7,"type":